review: Writing this review after visiting many dentists over the past 15 years or so in and around Nerul and Seawoods. I recently took my wife to this dental clinic, and our experience was outstanding. From start to finish, the process was smooth, and the dentist handled the root canal with exceptional ease and confidence. The care and expertise demonstrated were truly impressive. We highly recommend this clinic for top-notch dental services. Five stars without a doubt!

review: Took my dad for consultation. He had tooth ache. Waiting time was less. She quickly gave diagnosis and suggested filling. We didn't have to take another appointment, she got it done right away within half hour. She was gentle and sensitive. Dad is usually scared of dental treatments, but this time he was quite comfortable and relaxed as she took him through the process sensitively and explained well patiently. Dad is very happy with the treatment and the issue was solved perfectly. Thank you.

review: Dr. Chaitali is a very professional and experienced Dentist. Her calm demeanour and pleasant personality puts the patient at ease right at the beginning. She is very clear in her opinion about the patients condition, and lays out the facts without ambiguity. She is easy to talk to and discuss the problems without inhibitions. My family and I have sought her consultation regularly, and we highly recommend her.
